\c 5
\s Ihubo likaDebora loBaraki
\p
\v 1 UDebora loBaraki indodana kaAbinowama basebehlabela\x + Eks. 15.1. Hlab. 18.\x* ngalolosuku besithi:
\p
\v 2 Ngenxa yokuphindisela kwezimpindiselo koIsrayeli\x + Dute. 32.42. 2 Sam. 22.48. Hlab. 18.47.\x*, nxa abantu bezinikela ngokuzithandela\x + 5.9. 2 Lan. 17.16.\x*, busisani iN\nd kosi\nd*!
\v 3 Zwanini makhosi, libeke indlebe ziphathamandla\x + Hlab. 2.2. Zaga 31.4. Dute. 32.1,3. Hlab. 2.10.\x*, mina, mina ngizahlabela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, ngihubele iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli.
\v 4 N\nd kosi\nd*, ekuphumeni kwakho eSeyiri\x + Dute. 33.2. Dute. 4.11.\x*, ekunyatheleni kwakho usuka ensimini yeEdoma\x + Hlab. 68.7.\x*, umhlaba wazamazama\x + Hlab. 68.8. 2 Sam. 22.8. Hlab. 18.7; 77.18. Nah. 1.5. Hab. 3.3,10.\x*, lamazulu athonta, lamayezi athontisa amanzi.
\v 5 Izintaba zageleza phambi kweN\nd kosi\x + Isa. 64.1,3. Dute. 4.11. Hlab. 97.5. Mika 1.4.\x*\nd*, iSinayi\x + Eks. 19.18.\x* le phambi kweN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli.
\v 6 Ensukwini zikaShamigari indodana kaAnathi\x + 3.31.\x*, ensukwini zikaJayeli\x + 4.17.\x*, izindlela zaphela\x + Levi 26.22.\x*, lababehamba ezindledlaneni bahamba ngezindlela ezimazombazombe.
\v 7 Izakhamizi zemakhaya zaphela\x + 5.11. Dute. 3.5.\x* koIsrayeli, zaphela, ngaze ngasukuma mina Debora, ngasukuma, unina koIsrayeli.
\v 8 Wakhetha onkulunkulu abatsha\x + Dute. 32.16. Hlu. 2.12,17.\x*, khona kwaba lempi emasangweni. Sabonwa yini isihlangu lomkhonto\x + 1 Sam. 13.19,22. Hlu. 4.3.\x* phakathi kwabazinkulungwane ezingamatshumi amane koIsrayeli?
\v 9 Inhliziyo yami ikubanikimithetho bakoIsrayeli, abazinikela ngokuzithandela phakathi kwabantu\x + 5.2.\x*. Busisani iN\nd kosi\nd*!
\v 10 Bagadi babobabhemi abamhlophe\x + Nani 22.21. Hlu. 10.4; 12.14. Zek. 9.9.\x*, bahlali besigcabha\x + Hlab. 107.32. Isa. 28.6.\x*, labahambi endleleni, khulumani.
\v 11 Elizwini labatshoki, phakathi kwezindawo zokukha amanzi\x + Gen. 24.11.\x*, lapho bayalandisa ngemisebenzi elungileyo yeN\nd kosi\nd*, imisebenzi elungileyo yezakhamizi zemakhaya zakoIsrayeli\x + 5.11. Dute. 3.5.\x*. Ngalesosikhathi abantu beN\nd kosi\nd* behlela emasangweni.
\v 12 Vuka\x + Hlab. 57.8.\x*, vuka, Debora! Vuka, vuka, khuluma ingoma! Sukuma Baraki, uthumbe abathunjiweyo bakho\x + Hlab. 68.18. Efe. 4.8.\x*, ndodana kaAbinowama.
\v 13 Khona yayenza insali yabusa phezu kwezinduna ebantwini\x + Hlab. 49.14.\x*; iN\nd kosi\nd* yangenza ngabusa phezu kwabalamandla.
\v 14 Kuvela koEfrayimi\x + 3.27.\x* impande yabo yayimelene loAmaleki\x + 3.13.\x*; emva kwakho, Bhenjamini, phakathi kwabantu bakho; kuvela kuMakiri\x + Nani 32.39,40.\x* kwehla abanikumthetho\x + Dute. 33.21.\x*, lakoZebuluni abadonsa ngentonga yombhali.
\v 15 Leziphathamandla zakoIsakari zaziloDebora; la\add njengo\add*Isakari, waba njalo uBaraki\x + 4.14.\x*; wathunjwa esigodini ngenyawo zakhe. Ekwehlukaneni kukaRubeni izinqumo zenhliziyo zazizinkulu.
\v 16 Wahlalelani phakathi kwezibaya\x + Gen. 49.14. Hlab. 68.13.\x* ukuzwa umhlanga wokukhaliselwa\x + Jer. 18.16.\x* izimvu\x + Nani 32.1.\x*? Izifunda zakoRubeni zaba lokuhlolwa okukhulu kwenhliziyo.
\v 17 UGileyadi wahlala ngaphetsheya kweJordani\x + Josh. 13.24,25,26,27,28.\x*. LoDani wahlalelani emikhunjini\x + Josh. 19.46.\x*? UAsheri wahlala ekhunjini lolwandle\x + Josh. 19.29,31.\x*, wahlala ethekwini.
\v 18 UZebuluni\x + 4.10.\x* uyisizwe esadela umphefumulo waso kwaze kwaba sekufeni, loNafithali, emiqolweni yensimu.
\v 19 Amakhosi afika alwa; khona amakhosi eKhanani alwa eThahanakhi\x + Josh. 12.21; 17.11. Hlu. 1.27. 1 Kho. 4.12. Josh. 21.25.\x* ngasemanzini eMegido\x + Josh. 12.21; 17.11. Hlu. 1.27. 1 Kho. 4.12; 9.15. 2 Kho. 9.27; 23.29,30. 2 Lan. 35.22. Zek. 12.11. Isam. 16.16.\x*; kawathathanga impango yesiliva\x + 4.15,16.\x*.
\v 20 Zisemazulwini zalwa, inkanyezi zisendleleni zazo zalwa loSisera.
\v 21 Isifula iKishoni sabakhukhula\x + 4.7.\x*, isifula sendulo, isifula iKishoni. Mphefumulo wami, unyathela ngamandla!
\v 22 Khona atshaya phansi amasondo amabhiza, ngokumatha, ukumatha kwabalamandla\x + Gen. 49.24.\x* bakhe.
\v 23 Qalekisani iMerozi, kutsho ingilosi yeN\nd kosi\nd*, qalekisani ngokuqalekisa abakhileyo kuyo, ngoba kabezanga\x + 21.5,9,10. Neh. 3.5.\x* kuncedo lweN\nd kosi\x + 1 Sam. 18.17; 25.28.\x*\nd*, kuncedo lweN\nd kosi\nd*, lamaqhawe.
\v 24 Uzabusiswa phezu kwabesifazana uJayeli umkaHeberi umKeni\x + 4.17.\x*; ubusisiwe phezu kwabesifazana ethenteni.
\v 25 Wacela amanzi\x + 4.19.\x*, wa\add m\add*nika uchago, waletha amasi ngomganu wobukhosi.
\v 26 Welulela isandla sakhe esikhonkwaneni\x + 4.21.\x*, lesandla sakhe sokunene esandweni sezisebenzi, wamtshaya uSisera, wachoboza ikhanda lakhe, wahlaba wabhoboza inhlafuno yakhe.
\v 27 Phakathi laphakathi kwenyawo zakhe wakhothama wawa walala; phakathi laphakathi kwenyawo zakhe wakhothama wawa, lapho akhothamela khona, wawa lapho efile echithekile.
\v 28 Unina kaSisera walunguza ngewindi\x + 2 Sam. 6.16.\x*, wanqolonga ngeminxibo yewindi\x + Zaga 7.6.\x* \add wathi\add*: Kungani inqola yakhe iphuza ukuza\x + Eks. 32.1.\x*? Kungani ephuzile amavili ezinqola zakhe?
\v 29 Izihlakaniphi zamakhosazana akhe zaphendula, yebo yena wazibuyisela impendulo yakhe \add wathi\add*:
\v 30 Kabatholanga yini bayaba impango\x + Eks. 15.9.\x*, intombazana, amantombazana amabili kuleyo laleyondoda, impango yamalembu aconjiweyo kaSisera, impango yamalembu aconjiweyo afekethisiweyo ngenalithi, amalembu amabili aconjiweyo afekethisiweyo ngenalithi, awentamo zomphangi?
\v 31 Ngokunjalo kazibhubhe zonke izitha zakho\x + Hlab. 83.9,10.\x*, N\nd kosi\nd*. Kodwa abayithandayo \add kababe\add* njengokuphuma kwelanga\x + 2 Sam. 23.4.\x* ngamandla alo\x + Hlab. 19.4,5.\x*.
\p Lelizwe lathula iminyaka engamatshumi amane\x + 3.11.\x*.
